016770*    IF WUSEC-IO-OK
016770*        MOVE RUSEC-SECUR-CLAS-ID     TO WGLOB-SECUR-CLAS-ID
016770*        MOVE RUSEC-BR-ID             TO WGLOB-USER-BRANCH-CODE
016770*        MOVE RUSEC-USER-RPT-DSTRB-CD TO WGLOB-USER-RPT-DSTRB-CD
016770*    ELSE
PF 13 *    IF NOT WUSEC-IO-OK
PF 13 *        SET LSIR-SERVER-ERROR        TO TRUE
PF 13 *MSG: USER SECURITY RECORD  (@1) NOT FOUND
PF 13 *        MOVE WGLOB-USER-ID           TO WGLOB-MSG-PARM (1)
