      *------------------
       7300-READ-BPFS-REC.
      *------------------

           MOVE WGLOB-SECUR-CLAS-ID          TO WBPFS-SECUR-CLAS-ID.
           MOVE LSIR-BPF-ID                  TO WBPFS-BPF-ID.

PF 13 * IF BPFS-RECORD IN WORKING STORAGE MATCHES THE ONE WE ARE ABOUT
PF 13 * TO READ, THEN DON'T BOTHER WITH THE I/O

PF 13      IF WBPFS-KEY = RBPFS-KEY
PF 13          GO TO 7300-READ-BPFS-REC-X
PF 13      END-IF.

           PERFORM  BPFS-1000-READ
               THRU BPFS-1000-READ-X.

           IF  WBPFS-IO-NOT-FOUND
               SET  LSIR-SECURITY-CHECK-FAILED  TO TRUE
      *MSG: PROCESS FLOW SECURITY RECORD (@1@2) NOT FOUND
               MOVE LSIR-SECUR-CLAS-ID       TO WGLOB-MSG-PARM (1)
               MOVE LSIR-BPF-ID              TO WGLOB-MSG-PARM (2)
PIRAEX* IF THE REQUEST COMES THROUGH P STEP INTERFACE THROW          
PIRAEX* SPECIAL MSG AND WRITE INTO AUDIT REPORT SINCE IT MAY BE      
PIRAEX* SECURITY VIOLATION          
PIRAEX*        MOVE 'XS00100002'             TO WGLOB-MSG-REF-INFO
PIRAEX         IF  LSIR-PRCES-BFCN-SESSION 
PIRAEX* WRITE TO AUDIT REPORT - SECURITY VIOLATION
PIRAEX             PERFORM  2490-1000-BUILD-PARM-INFO
PIRAEX                 THRU 2490-1000-BUILD-PARM-INFO-X
PIRAEX*TEXT: P-STEP INTERFACE:SECURITY CLASS @1 NOT AUTHORIZED    
PIRAEX             MOVE '00001'              TO WS-TXT-SRC-REF-ID
PIRAEX             MOVE WGLOB-SECUR-CLAS-ID  TO L2490-TXT-PARM (1)
PIRAEX             PERFORM  9600-OUTPUT-USAU-RECORD
PIRAEX                 THRU 9600-OUTPUT-USAU-RECORD-X
PIRAEX*MSG: INTERNAL DATA SETUP PROBLEM- PLEASE CONTACT SYSTEMS
PIRAEX             MOVE 'XS00660018'         TO WGLOB-MSG-REF-INFO
PIRAEX         ELSE 
PIRAEX*MSG: PROCESS FLOW SECURITY RECORD (@1@2) NOT FOUND
PIRAEX             MOVE 'XS00100002'         TO WGLOB-MSG-REF-INFO
PIRAEX         END-IF 
               PERFORM  0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE
                   THRU 0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE-X
               GO TO  7300-READ-BPFS-REC-X
           END-IF.
      *
      *  RETURN PROCESS FLOW LEVEL INFORMATION TO THE CLIENT
      *
013578     IF  RBPFS-BPF-SECUR-AUD-NO
013578         SET WGLOB-AUDIT-NOT-REQUESTED TO TRUE
PF 13 *        MOVE WGLOB-BPF-SECUR-AUD-IND  TO LSIR-BPF-SECUR-AUD-IND
013578     END-IF.
013578     MOVE RBPFS-MSG-SECUR-CLAS-CD      TO WGLOB-MSG-SECUR-CLAS-CD.
PF 13 *    MOVE RBPFS-MSG-SECUR-CLAS-CD      TO LSIR-MSG-SECUR-CLAS-CD.

       7300-READ-BPFS-REC-X.
           EXIT.

