       7400-READ-BFCN-REC.
      *------------------

           MOVE WS-MIR-BUS-FCN-ID        TO WBFCN-BUS-FCN-ID.

           PERFORM  BFCN-1000-READ
               THRU BFCN-1000-READ-X.

           IF  WBFCN-IO-NOT-FOUND
               SET  LSIR-SERVER-ERROR    TO  TRUE
               MOVE WBFCN-BUS-FCN-ID     TO WGLOB-MSG-PARM (1)
      *MSG: BUSINESS FUNCTION ID (@1) NOT FOUND
               MOVE 'XS00100004'         TO WGLOB-MSG-REF-INFO
               PERFORM  0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE
                   THRU 0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE-X
               GO TO  7400-READ-BFCN-REC-X
           END-IF.
      *
      *  RETURN TRANSACTION LEVEL INFORMATION TO THE CLIENT
      *
           MOVE RBFCN-BUS-FCN-PDRVR-ID       TO WGLOB-MAIN-PGM-ID.
013578     MOVE RBFCN-BUS-FCN-AUD-IND        TO WGLOB-BPF-SECUR-AUD-IND.

       7400-READ-BFCN-REC-X.
           EXIT.

